## Color Palette (Single Source of Truth)

**Use these colors:**

- **Page background**: `bg-[#0B0E14]`
- **Card/Panel**: `bg-[#151921]`
- **Input**: `bg-[#131A23]` or `bg-[#11161D]`
- **Primary accent**: `text-[#0066cc]` / `bg-[#0066cc]`
- **Accent hover**: `hover:bg-[#0052a3]` / `hover:text-[#0052a3]`
- **Text**: Headings `text-white`, body `text-gray-400`, metadata `text-gray-500`, muted `text-gray-600`

**Borders:**
- Structural: `border-white/5`
- Card: `border-white/5` or `border-white/10`
- Interactive: `border-white/15` or `border-white/20`

**Guidance:** Prefer palette; check existing components first; add colors for data viz or status; consider adding new standards to this list.

