## Typography Patterns

### Section Headings (H2)
- `text-3xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight`, margin `mb-2`–`mb-6`. Responsive: `text-2xl md:text-3xl`.

### Page Titles (H1)
- `text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight leading-tight mb-8` (hero) or `text-4xl md:text-5xl` (project pages).

### Metadata Labels / Kickers
- `text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-500 font-mono` (or `text-xs`, `tracking-wider`). Accent: `text-blue-400`.

### Body Text
- `text-base md:text-lg text-gray-400 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl` (or `max-w-3xl`).

---

## Spacing Rhythm

**Vertical:** Section `py-24` (standard), `py-12 md:py-20` (alternate). Gaps: `space-y-12` (timeline), `space-y-6` (cards), `space-y-4` (tight). Margins: `mb-6 md:mb-8` (headings), `mb-4` (subheadings), `mb-2` (tight).

**Horizontal:** Container `px-6 lg:px-8` (outer), `px-4` or `px-6` (inner). Grid: `gap-4` (cards), `gap-6` (sections), `gap-8 md:gap-12` (large).

